hadiths[171]{hadithnumber,text}:
2137,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : insan ka behtareen khana wo hai jo uski kamai sey (hasil) ho. aur uski aulad bhi uski kamai hai."
2138,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Madi Karb Zubaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi aadmi apney haath ki kamai sey ziyada pakizah (aur umda) rozi hasil nahin kar sakta. aur aadmi apni zaat par, apney biwi bachchon par aur apney khaadimon par jo kuchh bhi kharch karta hai, wo sadqa hota hai."
2139,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : diyanat daar, sachcha musalman taajir qiyamat key din shaheedon key sath hoga."
2140,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bewa aur miskeen (ki zarooriyaat puri kerney) key liye daud dhoop karney wala , Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ki tarah hai, aur us shakhs ki tarah hai jo raat ko qiyam karta aur din ko roza rakhta hai."
2141,"Hazrat Muaz bin Abdullah (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu)) sey aur wo apney chacha (Hazrat Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney farmaya : hum log eik majlis mein mojud they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye. aap key sar Mubarak par pani ka asar tha (ghusl farma kar tashrif laye they). baaz logon ney arz kiya : aaj hum aap ko khush dekh rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : haan, Allah ka shukar hai. phir logon ney khushhali (aur dolat mandi) ka zikr chhed diya to aap ney farmaya : muttaqi aadmi key liye dolat-mand honey mein harj nahin. aur muttaqi key liye sehat dolat sey behtar hai. aur tabiat ka khush hona bhi (Allah) ki nemat hai."
2142,"Hazrat Abu-Humed (munzir bin Saad) Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : duniya key husool key liye achchha tariqa ikhtiyar karo. har insan key liye wo kaam aasan ho jata hai jis key liye wo paida kiya gaya hai."
2143,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey ziyada pareshani us momin ko hoti hai jo apni duniya key maamlat ki bhi fikr karta hai aur apni aakhirat key maamlat ki bhi. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees gharib hai. isey sirf Ismail (bin Behram) ney riwayat kiya hai."
2144,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey logo ! Allah sey daro aur achchhey tareeqey sey (aetidaal (darmiyaani raaste) key sath) rozi talab karo kyonkey koi insan apna rizq pura kiye baghair nahin mareyga agar-che us (rizq key husool) mein der ho jaey. chunanche Allah sey daro aur achchhey tareeqey sey rozi talab karo. jo halal hai, wo ley lo aur jo haram hai, wo chhod do."
2145,"Hazrat Qais bin Abu Ghazraa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamanaey Mubarak mein dalaal kahlaatey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas sey guzrey to aap ney hamara us sey behtar naam rakh diya . aap ney farmaya : aey taajiron ki jamaat ! kharid aur farokht mein qasmen khai jati hain aur fuzul baaten ho jati hain, (isliye) iskey sath sath sadqa bhi kartey raha karo."
2146,"Hazrat Ismail bin Ubaid apney walid (Hazrat Ubaid bin Rifaa) (Raziallahu anhuma) sey aur wo unkey dada (apney walid) Hazrat Rifaa bin Raafey bin Malik (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat karte hain, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath bahar gaey. log subah key waqt kharid aur farokht mein mashghool they. aap ney unhen aawaz di : aey taajiron ki jamaat ! . jab un logon ney apni nazren uthaeyn aur gardanen lambi kin (aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mutawajjeh ho gaey) to aap ney farmaya : taajir log qiyamat key din faajir (badkaar) (aur gunahgaar) bin kar uthengey , siwaye uskey jo Allah sey darta raha aur usney neki ki aur sach bola (yani jhoot aur dhokey sey perhez kiya)."
2147,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey kisi janib sey (kisi peshey, ilaqey, mlazimat waghera sey) kuchh (rizq) miley to usey chahiye ke us (peshey waghera) ko ikhtiyar kiye rakhey."
2148,"Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Sham aur Misr ki taraf samane tijarat bheja karta tha, (eik baar) mainey Iraaq ki taraf saman bhej diya, phir main Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : Ummul-mominin ! main Sham ki taraf saman bheja karta tha. ab mainey Iraaq ki taraf saman bheja hai. unhoney farmaya : aisa na karo, tumharey (sabiqa (pichhle)) maqame tijarat ko kya ho gaya? mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshade Mubarak suna hai : jab Allah Taala tum mein sey kisi key liye eik taraf sey rizq ka sabab paida karey to wo usey us waqt tak tarak na karey jab tak is mein badlaaw ya kharabi paida na ho jaey."
2149,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney koi Nabi aisa nahin bheja jo bakriyan charaney wala na ho. Sahaba kiram ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap bhi (galla-baani kartey rahey hain)?  aap ney farmaya : main bhi (bakriyan charaataa raha hun). meain qeeraaton key badley main Makka walon ki bakriyan charaayaa karta tha. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad) Hazrat Suwed bin Saeed (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : yani har bakri (ki dekh bhaal) ki ujrat eik qeeraat hoti thi."
2150,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Hazrat Zakariya (Alaihissalam) badhai they."
2151,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba taswiren bananey walon ko qiyamat key din azab hoga. unhen kaha jaeyga jo kuch tum ney (apney khayal key mutabiq) paida kiya tha, usey zinda bhi karo."
2152,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey ziyada jhoot bolney waley rangrez aur zargar (sunaar) hotey hain."
2153,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bazar mein maal laney waley ko rizq milta hai aur zakhira andozi karney wala maloon hai."
2154,"Hazrat Maamar bin Abdullah bin Nazlaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : gunah-gaar hi zakhira andozi karta hai."
2155,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : jo musalmanon sey khaney peeney ki chizon ki zakhira andozi kerega, Allah Taala usey juzaam aur iflaas (kodh aur kangaali) mein mubtala kerega."
2156,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hum tees sawaron ko eik fauji muhim par bheja. (raastey mein) hum kuchh logon key yahan (un ki basti mein) thehrey. hamney un sey khana manga. unhoney (hamari mehmani karney sey) inkar kar diya. (phir aisa huwa ke) unkey sardar ko bichchhu ney kaat liya , chunanche wo log hamarey paas aaye aur kaha : kya tum mein sey koi shakhs bichchhu kaatey ka dam kar sakta hai? mainey kaha : haan, main (kar sakta hun) lekin jab tak tum hamein bakriyan nahin dogey main usey dam nahin karunga. unhoney farmaya : hum tumhen tees bakriyan dengey (tum dam kar do). hamney un ki ye pesh kaash! qubul kar li. mainey saat baar Sura Fatiha padh kar us (mareez) par dam kiya to wo sehat yaab ho gaya aur hamney bakriyan wasul kar lin, phir hamarey dil mein shak paida huwa. (maloom nahin, ye bakriyan lena jayez tha ya nahin) hamney kaha : jaldi na karo yahan tak key hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho jaeyn. jab hum log khidmat mein hazir huye to mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya ke mainey ye kaam kiya hai. aap ney farmaya : kya tujhey malum na tha ke ye (surat) dam hai? bakriyan taqseem kar lo aur mera bhi hissa rakho. dusri do sanadon sey bhi ye riwayat Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam abu-Adbullah (Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah)) ney (oopper mazkur do sanadon mein Abu-Saeed Khudri sey bayan karney waley key barey mein raaey detey huye ( kaha : sahih ye hai ke wo ( ibn mutawakkil nahin balke ( abu-Mutwakkil hai."
2157,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey as-haabe suffa (Raziallahu anhum) mein sey chand afrad ko Quran ki aur likhney ki taalim di. un mein sey eik aadmi ney tohfey key tor par mujhey eik kamaan dey di. mainey ye soch kar ley li ke ye koi maal to hai nahin, aur main Allah ki raah mein (jihad kartey huye) is sey teer chalaaunga. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey uskey barey mein daryaft kiya to aap ney farmaya : agar tujhey ye baat pasand hai ke iskey badley tujhey (jahannam ki) aag ka toq pehnaya jaey to qubul kar ley."
2158,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey eik aadmi ko Quran padhaya. usney mujhey tohfey key tor par eik kamaan di. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat batai to aap ney farmaya : agar tu ney ye ley li to aag ki kamaan li. chunanche mainey wo wapis kar di."
2159,"Hazrat Abu-Masood (Aqba bin Amr Ansari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey ki qeemat, tawayaf ki ujrat aur kaahin ka nazrana leney sey mana farmaya."
2160,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey ki qeemat aur nasal kushi key janwer (saand) chhodney ki ujrat leney sey mana farmaya hai."
2161,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney billi ki qeemat leney sey mana farmaya hai."
2162,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney seengi lagwaai aur usey (seengi lagwaaney waley ko) uski ujrat ata farmaai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : is riwayat ko sirf ibne-Abi umr hi ney bayan kiya hai.
2163,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney seengi lagwaai aur mujhey hukm diya to mainey seengi laganey waley ko uski ujrat ada ki."
2164,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney seengi lagwaai aur seengi laganey waley ko uski ujrat ata farmaai."
2165,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Aqba bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney seengi laganey waley ki kamai sey mana farmaya."
2166,Hazrat Haram bin Mahisa (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Saad bin Mahisa bin Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey huye farmatey hain ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey seengi laganey waley ki kamai key mutalliq daryaft kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen is sey mana farmaya. unhoney apney hajat mand (aur muflis) honey ka zikr kiya to aap ney farmaya : uska apney oonton ko chaara khila do.
2167,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Fateh Makka key saal Makka mein farmaya : Allah Taala ney aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sharab , murdar , khinzir aur buton ki farokht haram kar di hai. us waqt aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! murda (janweron) ki charbi key barey mein farmaiye, us sey kashtiyon ko chikna kiya jata hai, chamdon ko lagaya jata hai (aur is tarah unhen qabile istimal banaya jata hai). aur log  (isey chiraghon mein jala kar) is sey roshni hasil kartey hain. aap ney farmaya : nahin, ye sab cheezen haram hain.  phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala yahudiyon ko tabah karey ! Allah ney un par charbi haram ki to unhoney usey pighla kar bech dala, aur uski qeemat kha gaey."
2168,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Asad bin Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney gaaney wali londiyan bechney aur kharidney sey, un ki kamai sey aur un ki qeemat khaney sey mana farmaya."
2169,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do qism ki bai (saude) sey mana farmaya hai : munaabiza sey aur mulaamisa sey."
2170,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mulaamisa aur munaabiza sey mana farmaya hai. (hadees ke raavi) Sehal ney apni riwayat mein ye izafa kiya hai ke Hazrat Sufiyan (bin Uena) (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mulaamisa ka matlab ye hai ke aadmi chiz ko (haath sey) chhuey aur usey (aakhon sey) na dekhey. aur munaabiza ka matlab ye hai ke yun kahey : tum apni chiz meri taraf phenk do aur main apni chiz tumhari taraf phenk deta hun."
2171,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi kisi ki bai (saude) par bai (sauda) na karey."
2172,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi apney bhai ki bai (saude) par bai (sauda) na karey."
2173,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney badha kar boli deney sey mana farmaya hai.
2174,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : boli na badhaao."
2175,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shehri dehati ki taraf sey bai (sauda) na karey."
2176,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shehri bahar waley ki taraf sey farokht na karey, logon ko chhod do ke Allah unhen eik doosrey key zariey sey rizq ata farmaaey."
2177,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya hai ke shehar wala dehat waley ki taraf sey farokht kerey. Hazrat Taaus (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey puchha : is irshad ka kya matlab hai ke shehar wala dehat waley ki taraf sey farokht na kerey? unhoney farmaya : yani uska dalaal na baney."
2178,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : saman laney waley taajiron ko (aagey ja kar) na milo. jo shakhs kisi (tajir) sey ja kar mila aur us sey (saman) kharid liya to Malik (bechney wala) jab bazar mein pahunchega to usey ikhtiyar hoga (ke soda qaaim rakhey ya mansookh kar dey)."
2179,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney saman laney walon ko aagey ja kar milney sey mana farmaya hai."
2180,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (dehat sey la kar cheezen) bechney walon ko )mandi mein pahunchney sey pehley) aagey ja kar milney sey mana farmaya.
2181,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do aadmi bai (sauda) keren to un mein sey har eik ko (us waqt tak) ikhtiyar hai jab tak wo eik doosrey sey juda na hon, aur ikatthey hon, ya unmein sey eik shakhs doosrey ko ikhtiyar na dey dey. agar eik ney doosrey ko ikhtiyar dey diya aur unhoney is shart par bai (sauda) ki to bai (sauda) wajib ho gaee. aur agar bai (sauda) key baad wo eik doosrey sey juda ho gaey, aur dono mein sey kisi ney bai (sauda) tarak na ki, tab bhi bai (sauda) wajib ho gaee."
2182,"Hazrat abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kharidney waley aur bechney waley ko ikhtiyar hai, jab tak wo eik doosrey sey juda na hon."
2183,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kharidney waley aur bechney waley ko ikhtiyar hai, jab tak wo eik doosrey sey juda na hon."
2184,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) sey darakhton key patton ki eik gathdi khareedi. jab bai (sauda) ho chuki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey ikhtiyar hai (bai (sauda) ko qaaim rakhey ya fasakh (radd) kar dey). Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney kaha : Allah aap jaisey soda karney waley ko lambi umr dey."
2185,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bai (sauda) bahami (aapsi) raza-mandi sey hoti hai.
2186,"Hazrat Qasim bin Abdur-Rehman (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah bin Masood) sey riwayat kartey huye farmatey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney sarkaari ghulamon mein sey eik ghulam Hazrat Ash'as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) key haath farokht kiya. baad mein unka aapas mein ikhtilaf ho gaya. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey aap ko (wo ghulam) bees hazar ka farokht kiya tha. Hazrat Ash'as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey aap sey das hazar ka kharid tha. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : agar aap chahen to main aap ko eik hadees sunaun jo mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni thi. unhoney kaha : suna dijiye. Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : jab bechney waley aur kharidney waley mein ikhtilaf ho jaey aur un mein sey kisi key paas gawah na ho, aur sauda hui chiz bilkul wesey hi mojud ho to bechney waley ka qol taslim kiya jaeyga (aur bai (sauda) qaaim rahegi) ya wo dono bai (saude) ko fasakh kar dengey. Ash'as (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mera khayal hai ke main ye soda fasakh (radd) kar dun, chunanche Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney bai (sauda) fasakh (radd) kar key ghulam wapis ley liya."
2187,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! eik shakhs mujh sey koi chiz khareednaa chahta hai jabkey wo chiz merey paas mojud nahin, kya main usey wo chiz bech dun? aap ney farmaya : jo chiz terey paas nahin, wo farokht na kar."
2188,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib (Rahimahullah) apney walid Shuaib bin Muhammad (Rahimahullah) sey , aur wo apney dada Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo chiz terey paas nahin, usey bechnaa jayez nahin, aur jiski zimme-daari qubul nahin ki gaee, is par nafa lena bhi jayez nahin."
2189,Hazrat itaab bin Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen Makka (governer bana kar) bheja to unhen us chiz ka nafa leney sey mana farmaya jiski zimmey daari qubul na ki gaee ho.
2190,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ya Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs do aadmiyon sey bai (sauda) kerey to wo un dono mein sey pehley aadmi ki hogi."
2191,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do sahibe-ikhtiyar bai (sauda) keren to bai (sauda) pehley ki hai."
2192,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bai (sauda) arbaan (bayaane key sath lain den kerney) sey mana farmaya hai.
2193,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bai (sauda) arbaan sey mana farmaya hai. abu-Adbullah (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah)) ney farmaya : bai (sauda) arbaan usey kehtey hain ke eik aadmi koi janwer so Dinar ka khareedey aur usey (bechney waley ko) do Dinar bayaana dey dey aur kahey : agar mainey ye janwer na kharid to ye do Dinar terey hongey. eik qol key mutabiq iska matlab. Allah ki qism aalam, ye hai ke aadmi koi bhi chiz khareedey aur bechney waley ko eik dirham ya us se kam aur ziyada (peshgi) ada kar dey aur kahey : agar mainey ye soda ley liya (aur bai (sauda) fasakh (radd) na ki) to theek hai warna ye dirham tera hoga."
2194,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dhokey ki bai (saude) aur kankari ki bai (saude) sey mana farmaya."
2195,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dhokey ki bai (saude) sey mana farmaya."
2196,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney janweron key pet key bachchey kharidney sey mana farmaya jab tak wo paida na ho jaeyn, aur unkey thanon mein mojud (doodh) ko kharidney sey mana farmaya magar maap kar, aur ghulam ko kharidney sey mana farmaya jabke wo bhagoda ho, aur ghanimat ki ashiya (cheezen) kharidney sey mana farmaya yahan tak key wo taqseem ho jaeyn, aur sadqaat ki ashiya (cheezen) kharidney sey mana farmaya yahan tak key wo (mustahiqeen key) qabzey mein aa jaeyn, aur ghota maarney waley key ghotey (sey hasil honey wali chiz ki peshgi kharidari) sey mana farmaya."
2197,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamila ka hamal bechney sey mana farmaya.
2198,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Ansari aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar (maali taawun (madad) ka) sawal kiya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tumharey ghar mein tumhari koi chiz mojud hai? usney kaha : ji haan ! eik kambal hai. hum aadha nichey bichhate hain aur aadha odh letey hain aur eik piyala hai jis mein pani peetey hain. aap ney farmaya : dono cheezen merey paas ley aao. wo unhen ley kar hazir huwa to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen apney haath mein liya aur farmaya : ye dono cheezen kon khareedtaa hai? eik aadmi ney kaha : main inhen eik dirham mein khareedtaa hun. aap ney do teen baar farmaya : eik dirham sey ziyada kon deta hai? eik aadmi ney kaha : main inhen do dirham mein khareedtaa hun. aap ney isey dono cheezen dey kar do dirham ley liye aur us Ansari Sabab ko dey diye, aur farmaya : eik dirham ka khaney peeney ka saman ley kar ghar walon ko dey do aur doosrey dirham ka kulhaada kharid kar merey paas lao. usney aisey hi kiya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kulhaada ley kar is mein apney haath sey dasta lagaya aur farmaya : jao (jangal sey) endhan ki lakdiyan laya karo (aur bech kar zarooriyaat puri karo) aur pandarah din tak main tumhen na dekhun. wo endhan la kar bechney laga. (uskey baad) wo hazir huwa to uskey paas das dirham (jama ho chukey) they. aap ney farmaya : kuchh raqam ka khaney ka saman kharid lo aur kuchh raqam ka kapda kharid lo. phir farmaya : ye kaam (mehnat sey rozi kamaana) terey liye us baat sey bahut behtar hai ke to qiyamat key din aaye to maangney ki wajeh sey tera chehra dagh daar ho. maangna sirf uskey liye jayez hai jisey muflisi (ghurbat) khaak-nasheen kar dey, ya jo intehai maqrooz ho, ya jo khoon ki wajeh sey pareshan ho (jis sey qatl sarzad ho gaya ho aur wo diyat ada karney ki taqat na rakhta ho)."
2199,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi musalman ka suda wapis kar lega to Allah Taala qiyamat key din uskey gunah maaf farma dega."
2200,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein (eik baar ashiya (cheezon) key) bhaaw chadh gaey. logon ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! bhaaw chadh gaey hain, aap (ashiya (cheezon) key) bhaaw muqarrar kar dijiye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala bhaaw muqarrar karney wala hai, wohi tangi karney wala, faraakhi karney wala aur raaziq hai. mujhey ummid hai ke main jab apney Rab sey miloonga to koi shakhs jaan aur maal key barey mein zulm ki bina par mujh sey koi mutalba karney wala nahin hoga."
2201,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamana Mubarak mein bhaaw chadh gaey to Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kaash! aap qimtein muqarrar farma detey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey ummid hai ke main tum sey juda hunga to koi shakhs mujh sey kisi zulm ki talaafi ka talab-gaar nahin hoga, jo zulm mainey is par kiya ho."
2202,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney eik aadmi ko jannat mein dakhil kar diya. wo bechtey waqt bhi narmi karta tha aur khareedtey waqt bhi."
2203,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala us bandey par reham farmaaey jo bechtey waqt narmi karta hai, khareedtey waqt narmi karta hai aur jab taqaza karta hai to narmi karta hai."
2204,"Hazrat Qeela Umme bani Anmaar (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key kisi Umerey key doran mein Marwa key qarib khidmat mein hazir hui. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main kharid aur farokht karney wali aurat hun. main jab koi chiz khareednaa chahti hun to main jo (qeemat ada karna) chahti hun, us sey kam par baat karti hun, phir badhtey badhtey us qeemat tak pahunch jati hun jo mera (asal) irada hota hai. aur jab main koi chiz bechnaa chahti hun to main jo (qeemat wasul karna) chahti hun, us sey ziyada ki baat karti hun, phir kam kartey kartey us qeemat tak pahunch jati hun jo mera irada hota hai (kya ye jayez hai)?  Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Qeela ! aisey na kiya karo. jab koi chiz khareednaa chaho to wohi qeemat pesh karo jo tumhara irada hai, chahey tumhen wo chiz (us qeemat par) miley ya na miley. aur farmaya : jab tum koi chiz bechnaa chaho to wohi qeemat talab karo jo tumhara irada hai, phir chahey (us qeemat par girahak key raza mand honey par) farokht karo (becho) ya (uskey raza mand na honey par) farokht na karo (becho)."
2205,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik ghazwey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. aap ney mujh sey farmaya : kya tum apna ye oont mujhey eik Dinar key iwaz farokht kartey ho? Allah tumhari maghfirat kerega. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! jab main Madina pahunch jaunga to ye oont aap ka huwa. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum isey merey haath do Dinar key iwaz farokht kartey ho? Allah tumhari maghfirat kerega. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke aap eik eik Dinar ka izafa farmatey rahey aur har Dinar key izaafey key sath farmatey : Allah tumhari maghfirat kerega. yahan tak key bees Dinar tak pahunch gaey. jab main Madina Munawra pahunch gaya to mainey oont ko uskey sar sey pakad kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kar diya. to aap ney farmaya : Bilal ! isey maale ghanimat mein sey bees Dinar dey do. (raqam ki adaegi key baad) aap ney mujh sey farmaya : apna oont ley lo aur isey apney ghar ley jao."
2206,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney suraj tulu honey sey pehley (kisi chiz ka) mol karney sey aur doodh deta janwer zibeh karney sey mana farmaya."
2207,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen aadmi aisey hain jin sey qiyamat key din Allah Taala kalam nahin farmaeyga , na un ki taraf dekhega , na unhen paak kerega, aur unkey liye dardnak azab hai. eik wo aadmi jis key paas sehra mein (chashmey waghera ka) pani, uski zarurat sey zayed hai aur wo musafir ko uskey istimal sey mana karta hai. (doosra) wo aadmi jisney Asr key baad kisi key haath soda bechaa aur Allah ki qism kha kar kaha ke usney itni qeemat mein isey kharid hai. kharidar ney isey sach samajh liya, halanke haqiqat uskey khilaf thi. aur (teesra) wo aadmi jo kisi Imam (Islaami hukmran) ki baiat karta hai aur wo sirf husoole duniya key liye uski baiat karta hai, agar Imam usey duniya (ka maal) dey dey to wafaa karta hai aur agar Imam usey duniya ka maal na dey to wo baiat par qaaim nahin rehta (Imam ki itaat nahin karta)."
2208,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen aadmiyon sey Allah Taala qiyamat key din kalam nahin farmaeyga, na un ki taraf dekhega, na unhen paak kerega, aur unkey liye dardnak azab hai. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo kon hain? wo to na-kaam rahey aur bahut khasarey mein rahey. aap ney farmaya : apna tehband (takhnon sey nichey tak) latkaaney wala, (koi chiz) dey kar ehsan jatlaaney wala aur jhooti qism kha kar apney maal ki raghbat (dilchaspi) dilaney wala."
2209,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada Haris bin Rabee Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : farokht kartey waqt qism khaney sey ijtinab (parhez) karo, ye sodey mein raghbat (dilchaspi) paida karti hai (jis sey pehley pehal soda ziyada biktaa hai), phir barkat ko khatam kar deti hai."
2210,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney phal aaya hua huwa khajoor ka darkht kharid to us (darkht) ka phal bechney waley ka hai agar ye ke kharidar shart kar ley (ke main darkht phal samet kharid raha hun). Imam Ibne-Maja ney Muhammad bin Rumeh key wastey sey bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mazkura baala hadees ki maanind bayan kiya."
2211,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney khajoor key darkht bechey jabke un ki taabeer ho chuki thi to unka phal bechney waley ka hai, siwaye us surat key ke kharidar shart kar ley. aur jisney koi ghulam kharid jis key paas kuch maal tha to uska maal bechney waley ka hai, siwaye is surat key ke kharidar shart kar ley."
2212,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs khajoor key darkht bechey aur ghulam bechey. Nafey (Rahimahullah) ney ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey dono jumley ikhattey (eik jumley ki surat mein) riwayat kiye."
2213,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla farmaya ke khajoor key darakhton ka phal taabeer karney waley ka hai, siwaye us surat key ke kharidar shart kar ley. aur ghulam ka maal bechney waley ka hai, siwaye us surat key ke kharidar shart kar ley."
2214,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal us waqt tak na becho, jab tak unka sahih hona zahir na ho jaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bechney waley aur kharidney waley (dono) ko mana farmaya."
2215,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phal na becho yahan tak key un ki salahiyat (aur durusti) zahir ho jaey."
2216,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney phal bechney sey mana farmaya yahan tak key un ki durusti zahir ho jaey."
2217,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney phalon ki farokht sey mana farmaya yahan tak key unka rang badal jaey, aur angooron ki farokht sey mana farmaya yahan tak key wo siyah ho jaeyn, aur ghalley (gehun aur jau waghera) ki farokht sey mana farmaya yahan tak key wo sakht ho jaey."
2218,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kaee saal ka (aainda paida honey wala) phal farokht karney sey mana farmaya.
2219,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs (baagh ka) phal farokht karey, phir is par aafat aa jaey to us (bechney waley)  ko chahiye ke apney bhai key maal sey kuchh na ley (uski qeemat wasul na karey). wo apney musalman bhai ka maal kis wajeh sey leta hai?"
2220,"Hazrat Suwed bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main aur Hazrat Mukhrifaa Abdi (Raziallahu anhu) Hijr (key shehar) sey kapda laye . hamarey paas Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur hum sey eik shalwaar ka soda kiya. hamarey paas eik tolney wala tha jo ujrat par tolta tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : aey tolney waley ! wazan kar, aur jhuktaa tol."
2221,"Hazrat Abu-Safwaan bin Umaira (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey hijrat sey pehley Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key haath eik paajaama farokht kiya. aap ney (uski qeemat key tor par sona , chaandi ya ghalla) mujhey tol kar ata farmaya aur jhuktaa huwa tola."
2222,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum tolo to jhuktaa huwa tolo."
2223,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to (Madiney key) logon ka maap intehai bura tha, phir Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai : (وَيْلٌ لِّلْمُطَفِّفِينَ),''maap tol mein kami karney walon key liye halakat hai.'' to unhoney achchhey tareeqey sey maapna shuru kar diya."
2224,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jo ghalla farokht kar raha tha. aap ney us (ghalley) mein haath dala to malum huwa ke is mein dhoka hai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo dhoka dey, wo hum mein sey nahin."
2225,"(Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda ghulam) Hazrat Abu Humraa (Hilal bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jis key paas eik bartan mein khaney ki chiz (gehun ya khajoor waghera) thi. aap ney is mein haath dala, phir farmaya : shayad tu ney dhoka kiya hai. jisney hamein dhoka diya, wo hum mein sey nahin."
2226,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs ghizaae jins (cheeze) khareedey to wo usey puri tarah wasul karney sey pehley na bechey."
2227,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs ghizaae jins (cheeze) khareedey to wo usey puri tarah wasul karney sey pehley na bechey. abu-Awaana apni riwayat mein bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : meri raey mein har chiz ka hukm ghizaae ajnaas (saaman) wala hi hai."
2228,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khaney ki chiz (ghalla waghera) farokht karney sey mana farmaya, jab tak usey do pemaney na maap lein : bechney waley ka pemana aur kharidney waley ka pemana."
2229,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log qaflon sey ghalla maapey toley baghair kharid letey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein is ko bechney sey mana farmaya yahan tak key uski jagah sey muntaqil kar lein."
2230,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main bazar mein khajuren bechaa karta tha. main(gaahak ko) kehta : mainey apney is pemaney sey maapaa hai ke ye is qadr (itney wasq) hai. main is maap ki bina par khajuren uskey hawaley karta aur apna munaafaa ley leta, phir mujhey is barey mein shak paida huwa to mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey daryaft kiya to aap ney farmaya : jab to pemaney ka naam ley to usey maap kar dey."
2231,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Basar Mazni (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : apna khana (ghalla waghera) maap liya karo, is main tumharey liye barkat hogi."
2232,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apna khana (ghalla waghera) maap liya karo, is main tumharey liye barkat hogi."
2233,"Hazrat abu-Usaid (Malik bin Rabeea Saaidi) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nabeet ke baazar mein tashrif ley gaey, usey dekha aur farmaya : ye tumhara bazar nahin. phir eik aur bazar mein tashrif ley gaey, usey dekha to farmaya : ye bhi tumhara bazar nahin. phir us bazar mein tashrif laye aur is mein ghoomey phirey, phir farmaya : ye tumhara bazar hai. isey kam na kya jaey aur is par tex (khiraaj) na lagaya jaey."
2234,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs subah key waqt Fajr ki namaz key liye jata hai, wo eman ka jhandaa ley kar jata hai. aur jo shakhs subah subah bazar jata hai, wo iblees ka jhandaa ley kar jata hai."
2235,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs bazar mein dakhil hotey waqt ye dua padhey : (لا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ يُحْيِي وَيُمِيتُ وَهُوَ حَيٌّ لَا يَمُوتُ بِيَدِهِ الْخَيْرُ كُلُّهُ وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ), ''akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, badshahi usi ki hai aur tareef bhi usi ki hai, wo zinda karta hai aur wohi maut deta hai, aur wo zinda rehney wala hai jisey maut nahin, usi key haath mein tamam ki tamam bhalai hai, aur wo har chiz par qadir hai.'' to Allah Taala uskey liye das lakh nekiyan likhtaa hai, aur das lakh gunah maaf farmata hai. aur uskey liye jannat main eik ghar taamir farmata hai."
2236,"Hazrat Sakhr bin Wdaa'a Ghaamidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! meri ummat key liye subah ka waqt ba-barkat bana dey. unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab koi fauji dasta ya lashkar rawana farmatey to subah key waqt rawana farmatey they. Hazrat Umaara bin Hadeed (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : Hazrat Sakhr (Raziallahu anhu) taajir they, wo apna tijaarati qafila subah key waqt rawana farmaya kartey they, chunanche wo khushhal ho gaey aur unka maal ziyada ho gaya."
2237,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! meri ummat key liye Jumerat ki subah mein barkat ata farma."
2238,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! meri ummat key liye subah key waqt mein barkat ata farma."
2239,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney aisa janwer kharid jis ka doodh roka gaya tha to usey teen din tak ikhtiyar hai (ke soda qaaim rakhey ya khatam kar dey) agar wo janwer ko wapis karey to uskey sath eik saa khajuren bhi dey, gehun na dey."
2240,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logo ! jisney doodh roka huwa janwer kharid liya, usey teen din tak (wapis karney ka) ikhtiyar hai. agar wo wapis karey to uskey sath uskey doodh ka dugna ada kerey. ya farmaya : uskey doodh ki qeemat ke barabar gehun ada karey."
2241,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main gawahi deta hun ke sach bolney waley , aur jinhen sachchi khabren di gaeen, (yani) Abul-Qaasim (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ney hamein hadees sunai aur farmaya : un mada janweron ki farokht dhoka hai jinka doodh roka gaya ho. aur musalman key liye dhoke bazi haram hai."
2242,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla jari farmaya ke ghulam ka faeyda us (key nuqsan) ki zimmey daari key sath hai."
2243,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney eik ghulam kharid aur us sey mazduri karwaai, phir us ghulam mein aeb malum huwa to usey wapis kar diya. bechney waley ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! usney merey ghulam sey mazduri karwaai hai (lihaza wo aamdani mujhey dilwaai jaey). to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : faeyda (nuqsan ki) zimmey-daari key sath hai."
2244,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghulam ki zimmey daari teen din tak hai."
2245,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaar din key baad (ghulam ki) koi zimmey daari nahin."
2246,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : musalman musalman ka bhai hai, aur jo musalman apney bhai key haath koi aeb daar chiz bechey uskey liye halal nahin ke uskey liye (wo aeb) bayan na karey."
2247,"Hazrat Waasila Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : jis shakhs ney bataey baghair aeb daar chiz bech di, wo hamesha Allah key ghazab mein mubtala rahega , aur farishtey is par hamesha lanat kartey rahengey."
2248,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein jab ghulam hazir kiye jatey to aap eik ghar key sab afrad (eik shakhs ko) ata farmatey, unkey darmiyan judai dalna pasand na farmatey."
2249,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do ghulam ata farmaaey jo aapas mein bhai they. mainey un mein sey eik bech diya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : un do ghulamon ka kya haal hai? mainey kaha : mainey un mein sey eik bech diya hai. aap ney farmaya : usey wapis ley lo."
2250,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us shakhs par lanat farmaai hai jo maa betey mein , ya bhai bhai mein judai daley."
2251,"Hazrat Abdul-Majeed bin Wahab (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke mujh sey Hazrat Ada bin Khalid bin Hauza (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kya main tujhey eik tehreer na padhaaun jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey ata farmaai thi? mainey kaha : ji haan. unhoney mujhey tehreer nikal kar dikhai. is mein ye alfaz likhey huye they : ye us chiz ki dastawez hai jo Ada bin Khalid bin Hauza (Raziallahu anhu) ney Muhammad Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey khareedi. usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey eik ghulam ya eik aisi londi khareedi hai jisey koi bimari nahin, koi buri aadat nahin aur na haram ka maal hai. ye bai eik musalman ki eik musalman sey hui hai.'"
2252,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs koi londi kharidey to ye dua padhey : (اللهم إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ خَيْرَهَا وَخَيْرَ ما جَبَلْتَهَا عَلَيْهِ وَأَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ شَرِّهَا وَشَرِّ ما جَبَلْتَهَا عَلَيْهِ)aey Allah ! main tujh sey uski bhalai maangta hun aur jin aadaton par tuney isey paida kya hai unki bhalai maangta hun. aur uskey shar sey teri panah mein aata hun aur jin aadaton par tu ney isey paida kya hai unkey shar sey teri panah mein aata hun. aur barkat ki dua kerey. aur jab koi shakhs oont khareedey to unki kohaan ki bulandi par haath rakh kar barkat ki dua karey aur wohi alfaz padhey."
2253,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : soney ka soney sey tabaadla sood hai magar jab dast badast ho (tab sood nahin), gehun ka gehun sey tabaadla sood hai siwaye uskey ke dast-badast ho, jo ka jo sey tabaadla sood hai magar jab dast badast ho, khajoor ka khajoor sey tabaadla sood hai illa ye ke dast badast ho."
2254,"Hazrat Muslim bin Yasar aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubaid (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : ( kisi safar mein) eik manzil par Hazrat Ubada bin Samit aur Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhuma) ki kisi girja ya (yahud key) Maabad mein baham (aapas mein) mulaqat ho gaee. Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ney ( haazirin ko) hadees sunatey huye farmaya : hamen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chaandi key badley mein chaandi ki, soney key badley mein soney ki, gehun key badley mein gehun ki, jo key badley mein jo ki, aur khajoor key badley mein khajoor ki, eik riwayat key mutabiq : aur namak key badley mein namak ki kharido-farokht karney sey mana farmaya. aur hamen jo key badley mein gehun ya gehun key badley mein jo ki dast badast bai karney ka hukm diya jaisey hum chahen (miqdaar ki kami beshi key sath.)"
2255,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaandi key badley mein chaandi, soney key badley mein sona, jo key badley mein jo , aur gehun key badley mein gehun barabar barabar ( tabaadla) hona chahiye ."
2256,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen adna qism ki khajuren inayat farmatey . hum unkey badley mein un sey behtar khajuren , ziyada narkh par kharid letey . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik saa khajuron ka do saa sey tabaadla ya eik dirham ka do dirahmon sey tabaadla jayez nahin . dirham key badley mein dirham aur Dinar key badley mein Dinar hota hai. un dono key darmiyan , siwaye wazan ki kami beshi key , koi fazilat nahin ."
2257,"Hazrat abu-Saaleh (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna ke dirham key badley mein dirham aur Dinar key badley mein Dinar hota hai. mainey kaha : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ko (uskey bar-aks) dusri baat kehtey suna hai. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey mila tha. mainey unhen kaha : aap sirf ( dirham o Dinar key tabaadley) key barey mein jo kuch farmatey hain, kya ye masla aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai ya Allah ki kitab mein (uskey barey mein) kuch dekha hai? to unhoney farmaya : mainey ye masla na Allah ki kitab mein paya hai, na Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai lekin mujhey Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) ney bataya tha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : sood sirf udhaar mein hota hai."
2258,"Hazrat Abu Jozaa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey) barahe-rast ( suna ke wo bai sarf ka hukm detey they) usey jayez kehtey they (aur un sey ye qol riwayat kya jata tha, phir mujhey khabar mili ke unhoney us qol sey ruju kar liya hai, chunanche main un sey Makka ja kar mila aur arz kya : mujhey khabar mili hai ke aap ney (Sarf key jawaz sey) ruju kar liya hai. unhoney farmaya : haan! wo qol meri apni raey thi. aur ye abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey hain ke aap ney bai sirf sey mana farmaya hai."
2259,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaandi key badley mein sona lena sood hai magar jab dast badast ho (phir nahin). abu-Bakar bin Abu-Sheba bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Sufiyan bin Uena (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : chaandi key badley mein sona, yad rakho ."
2260,"Hazrat Malik bin Aus bin Hadsan (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey (kisi majlis mein) aa kar kaha : hamen (dinaron key) badley mein dirham kon dega? to Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif farma they. unhoney farmaya : hamen apna sona dikhao , phir jab hamara khazaanchi aayega to hamarey paas aana, hum aap ko aap ki chaandi (dirahmon ki surat mein) ada kerengey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : qism hai Allah ki! aisey nahin ho sakta , aap usey chaandi (abhi) ada keren, ya uska sona usey wapis kar den kyonkey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : soney key badley mein chaandi ( lena ya dena) sood hai magar dast badast jayez hai."
2261,"Hazrat umr bin Muhammad bin Ali bin abi Talib apney walid (Hazrat Muhammad bin hanfiya (Rahimahullah)) sey aur wo unkey dada (aur apney walid Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Dinar key badley mein Dinar hai aur dirham key badley mein dirham. un mein koi kami beshi ( jayez ) nahin . jis ko chaandi ki zarurat ho, wo soney key badley mein usey hasil kar ley, aur jisey soney ki zarurat ho, wo chaandi key iwaz tabaadla kar key ley ley . aur sirf (dirham o Dinar ka bahami (aapsi) tabaadla) haathon haath hota hai."
2262,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main oont becha karta tha. main chaandi key badley mein sona, soney key badley mein chaandi , dirahmon key badley mein Dinar aur dinaron key badley mein dirham ley liya karta tha, phir mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey daryaft kya to Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : jab eik chiz ley aur dusri dey to apney sathi sey juda na ho jab tak maamla saaf na ho jaey . ye riwayat eik dusri sanad sey Saeed bin Juber key shagirdon sey shak key baghair Samak bin Harab key wastey sey ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey marvi hai."
2263,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney musalmanon ka raaij sikka bila zarurat todney sey mana farmaya hai.
2264,qabila banu zohra key Mola Hazrat Abu-Ayash Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey jau ko Sulat key iwaz kharidney ka masla puchha to Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : un mein behtar jins kon si hai? Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : (mainey kaha) jo . to Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey us tabaadley sey mana farma diya aur farmaya : mainey khud suna ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey khushk khajoor key iwaz taza khajoor kharidney key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : kya taza khajoor khushk ho kar (wazan mein) kam ho jati hai? Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : ji haan . to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us bai sey mana farma diya .
2265,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bai mazaabna sey mana farmaya. mazaabna ka matlab ye hai ke aadmi apney baagh ka phal us andaz sey farokht karey ke khajoor key darakhton ka phal khushk khajuron key iwaz maap kar bechey. aur angoor ki belon ka phal kishmish key iwaz maap kar bechey, aur khet (ki fasal) ghalley key iwaz maap kar farokht kerey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sab Suraton sey mana farmaya."
2266,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya.
2267,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya."
2268,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney araaya key barey mein rukhsat di hai."
2269,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ariya ko uskey andazey key barabar khushk khajoor key iwaz farokht karney ki ijazat di. Hazrat Yahya bin Saeed (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : araaya ka ye matlab hai ke aadmi khajoor key chand darakhton ka taza phal andazey sey apney ghar ki khushk khajuron key iwaz kharid ley."
2270,Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hewaan ki hewaan sey udhaar bai sey mana farmaya.
2271,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik janwer ka do janweron sey dast badast tabaadla karney mein koi harj nahin . aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (is qism ka tabaadla) udhaar key sath napasand farmaya."
2272,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Safeeya (Raziallahu anha) ko saat ghulamon key iwaz kharid tha. Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi (Rahimahullah) ney is hadees mein ye alfaz bhi bayan farmaai : Hazrat dahiya kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) sey .
2273,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis raat mujhey meraaj hui, (us safar key doran mein) mera guzar aisey afrad key paas sey huwa jinkey pet makaanon ki tarah (badey badey) they, un (peton) mein sanp bharey huye they jo unkey un key peton key bahar sey nazar aa rahey they. mainey kaha : Jibril ! ye kon log hain? Jibril (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : ye sood khaney waley hain."
2274,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sood key sattar gunah hain jin mein sab sey halka gunah is qadr (bada) hai jaisey koi shakhs apni maa sey nikah kerey."
2275,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sood key tehattar darwazey hain."
2276,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : sab sey aakhir mein sood ki aayat nazil hui aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski tashreeh karney sey pehley faut ho gaey, isliye sood ko bhi chhod do aur mashkook surat sey bhi perhez karo."
2277,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sood khaney waley par, sood deney waley par , uskey gawahon par aur uski tehreer likhney waley par lanat farmaai hai."
2278,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon par zarur aisa zamana aayega jis mein koi shakhs sood khaye baghair nahin rahega . jo shakhs sood nahin khayega usey bhi uska gardo ghubar to pahunch hi jaeyga."
2279,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sood key zariey sey maal mein izafa kerega, uska anjame-kaar maal ki qillat hoga."
2280,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Madina munawwara) tashrif laye to log do-do teen-teen saal pehley raqam dey kar khajuren kharid letey they to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs khajuron ki bai salaf karey to usey chahiye ke malum maap aur malum tol key sath malum muddat key liye bai salaf kerey."
2281,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : falan log musalman ho gaey hain, unka talluq Yahud sey hai aur wo bhookey hain (un key paas khurak mojud nahin) mujhey khatra hai ke wo (bhook ki wajeh sey) murtad ho jaeyngey. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi key paas (kuchh maal) mojud hai? eik Yahudi ney kaha : merey paas itni miqdaar hai (usney chiz ka naam bhi liya tha) usney ghaaliban kaha : teen sau Dinar. (aur kaha ke main iskey iwaz) falan bhaaw sey, falan baagh sey (wasul karunga) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : falan bhaaw sey, itni muddat key udhaar par, lekin falan baagh sey nahin (baagh key ta'yun ki shart na lagaeyn)."
2282,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu Mujaalid ya Abu Majaalid sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Shaddad aur Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhuma) ka bai-salam key barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya. unhoney mujhey Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bheja. mainey (un ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar) un sey daryaft kiya to unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ehad Mubarak mein aur Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key zamanae Mubarak mein gehun , jau , munaqqa aur khajoor un logon sey peshgi raqam dey kar kharid letey they jinkey paas (us waqt) wo cheezen nahin hoti thin. unhoney farmaya : mainey Abdur-Rehman bin Abzi (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ye masla puchha to unhoney bhi yehi farmaya."
2283,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to kisi chiz ki baie-salaf karey to usey dusri chiz (ke saude) sey tabdeel na kar. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney yehi riwayat Shujaa bin Waleed key doosrey shagrid Abdullah bin Saeed ki sanad sey bhi isi tarah bayan ki lekin is mein Ziyad bin Khaseema aur Atiya key darmiyan Saad ka wasta bayan nahin kiya."
2284,"Najraani sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey kaha : kya main khoshey nikalney sey pehley khajuron key darakhton ki baie-salam kar liya karun? unhoney farmaya : nahin ! mainey kaha : kyon? unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik shakhs ney khajuron key darakhton par khoshey zahir honey sey pehley khajuron key eik baagh ki baie-salam ki. us saal baagh mein phal na laga. kharidar ney kaha : khoshey aaney tak ye baagh mera hai. bechney waley ney kaha : mainey tujhey ye baagh eik saal key liye farokht kiya tha. unhoney apna muqadma Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya to aap ney bechney waley sey kaha : kya usney terey darakhton sey kuchh (phal ya rupya) wasul kiya hai? usney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : to phir uska maal apney liye kis tarah halal samajhta hai? us sey jo kuchh liya hai, wo usey wapis kar dey aur (aainda) khajoor key darakhton ki bai-salam na kiya karo jab tak uski salahiyat zahir na ho jaey."
2285,"Hazrat Abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey jawan oont qarz liya aur farmaya : jab zakat key oont ayengey, hum tujhey (eik oont) ada kar dengey. jab oont aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : abu-Raafey ! us shakhs ko uska jawan oont ada kar do. lekin mujhey chaar daant ya us sey ziyada umr wala oont hi mila. mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (soorate haal sey) aagah kiya to aap ney farmaya : wohi dey do, behtareen log wo hotey hain jo achchhey tareeqey sey (qarz) ada kartey hain."
2286,"Hazrat Arbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney arz kiya : mujhey mera oont ada farma dijiye. Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney isey badi umr ka oont ata farmaya to usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! iski umr to merey oont sey ziyada hai (aur ye ziyada qeemti hai). Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtareen log wo hotey hain jo achchhey tareeqey sey (qarz) ada karen."
2287,"Hazrat Saaib bin Saifii Makhzoomi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha : aap zamanae jahiliyat mein merey shareek they to aap behtareen shareek they. aap na mujh sey muqabla kartey they, na jhagda kartey they."
2288,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey , Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney aur Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ney jange Badr key din hasil honey waley maale ghanimat mein sharaakat ki. main aur Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) kuchh na laye, jabke Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu)) kuffar key (do aadmi) giraftar kar key (ley aaye). jo hum teeno key mushtarka ghulam huye."
2289,"Hazrat Saleh bin Suheb bin Sanan (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Suheb Romi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen chizon mein barkat hai : udhaar bechnaa , muqaarza, aur ghar mein istimal key liye gehun mein jau mila lena, bechney key liye nahin."
2290,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara behtareen khana wo hai jo tumhari kamai sey (hasil) ho. aur tumhari aulad bhi tumhari kamai hai.
2291,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey paas kuchh maal hai aur meri aulad bhi hai. aur mera baap mera sara maal ley lena chahta hai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to bhi aur tera maal bhi terey baap hi ka hai.
2292,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : merey walid ney mera sara maal ley liya hai. to aap ney farmaya : to aur tera maal terey baap ka hai.  aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye bhi farmaya hai : tumhari aulad tumhari behtareen kamai mein sey hai, isliye unkey maal sey kha liya karo."
2293,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Hind binte Utba bin Rabiaa‬ (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! (merey shohar) Hazrat Abu-Sufiyaan paisa sanbhaal kar rakhney waley aadmi hain. wo mujhey itna (kharch) nahin detey jo mujhey aur merey bachchon ko kafi ho, siwaye uikey ke main un ki la ilmi mein unkey maal mein sey kuchh ley lun (tab guzaara ho sakta hai) to aap ney farmaya : itna ley lo jo tumhen aur tumhari aulad ko munasib had tak kafi ho."
2294,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab aurat (ghar key halaat mein) kharabi kiye baghair khawind key ghar sey kharch karey (riwayat key Raavi Muhammad bin Abdullah ney kaha) merey baap ney apni hadees mein bayan kiya : jab khana khilaaey to usey us (key amal) ka sawab milega , aur mard ko uski kamai honey ki wajeh sey itna hi sawab milega, aur aurat ko (Fi sabilillah) kharch karney ka sawab milega, aur (maal ki hifazat aur kharch key zimmedar) khazaanchi ko bhi itna hi sawab milega. unkey sawab mein (eik doosrey key sawab ki wajeh sey) koi kami nahin ki jaeygi."
2295,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : aurat apney ghar ki koi chiz khawind ki ijazat key baghair kharch na kerey. haazirin ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! khana bhi nahin? aap ney farmaya : wo to hamara umda maal hai."
2296,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghulam ki dawat qubul kar liya kartey they."
2297,"Hazrat Aabiul-Laham (Raziallahu anhu) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Umer (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey aaqa mujhey (khaney ki) koi chiz detey to main (doosron ko) khila deta. unhoney mujhey mana kiya. ya farmaya : unhoney mujhey maara. mainey ya unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (is soorate-haal key mutalliq) daryaft kiya. mainey kaha : main to us kaam sey baaz nahin aaunga . ya (kaha) main ye kaam tarak nahin karunga to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sawab tum dono ko milega."
2298,"bano ghabar qabiley key eik fard Hazrat Ibaad bin Shurehbil (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik saal hamarey yahan qehat pad gaya, main Madiney aaya. wahan eik khet mein chala gaya aur kuchh khoshey tod kar daney nikal kar kha liye aur (kuchh daney) apni chadar mein dal liye. khet waley ney aa kar mujhey maara aur mera kapda chin liya. mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar shikayat ki to aap ney us aadmi sey farmaya : wo bhookaa ya thakaa huwa tha tu ney isey khana nahin khilaya. wo (masley sey) na-waqif tha tu ney isey taalim nahin di . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey us shakhs ney kapda wapis kar diya. aur aap ney isey eik aadha wasq ghalla bhi dilwaya."
2299,"Hazrat Raafey bin Amr Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab main ladka tha to main (eik baar) apney khajuron key darakhton par, ya farmaya : Ansaar key darakhton par patthar maar raha tha. mujhey (pakad kar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : ladkey ! ya farmaya : beta ! to darakhton par patthar kyon maarta hai? mainey kaha : khaney key liye . aap ney farmaya : darakhton par patthar na phenka kar, jo khajuren nichey giri hui hon, wo kha liya kar. phir merey sar par haath pher kar farmaya : aey Allah ! iska pet bhar dey."
2300,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to kisi charwahey (key rewad) key paas sey guzrey to us (charwahey) ko teen baar aawaz dey. agar wo tujhey jawab dey to theek hai (us sey ijazat ley ley) warna kharabi kiye baghair (bakri ka doodh hasabe zarurat) pi ley. jab tera guzar kisi baagh key paas sey ho to baagh waley ko teen baar aawaz dey. agar wo ijazat dey to behtar warna (baagh ka phal hasabe zarurat) kha ley lekin kharabi na karna."
2301,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs kisi baagh key paas sey guzrey to is mein sey kha sakta hai lekin kapdon mein chhupa kar na ley jaey."
2302,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (khitab farmaney key liye) khadey huye aur farmaya : koi shakhs kisi key janwer ka doodh bila ijazat na ley. kya tum mein sey kisi ko ye baat achchhi lagti hai ke koi uskey kamrey mein aa kar uskey ghalla mehfooz rakhney ki jagah ka darwaza todey aur ghalla nikal kar ley jaey? logon key janweron key thanon mein un (malikon) ki khurak mehfooz hoti hai, isliye koi aadmi kisi shakhs ka janwer uski ijazat key baghair na dohey ."
2303,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik safar mein hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they. (raastey main eik jagah) hamen keekar key darakhton taley kuchh than bandhi oontniyaan nazar aayin. hum unkey paas jama ho gaey. (us par) hamein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aawaz di to hum aap key paas wapis aagaey. aap ney farmaya : ye oontniyaan eik musalman gharaney ki hain. Allah key baad yehi unkey liye khurak ka zariya aur barkat ka baais hain. kya tumhen ye baat achchhi lagti hai ke tum apney tosha daanon key paas pahuncho to dekho ke un mein jo kuchh tha, koi ley gaya hai? kya tum isey insaf samajhtey ho? ,Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : nahin. aap ney farmaya : ye maamla bhi aisa hi hai. hamney arz kiya : agar hamein khaney peeney ki zarurat ho to (hum kya keren)? aap ney farmaya : kha lo aur sath na ley jaao, pi lo aur sath na ley jaao."
2304,"Hazrat Umme-Haani (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen farmaya : bakriyan paalo, un mein barkat hai."
2305,"Hazrat Urwa bin Ja'ad Baarqi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : oont apney malikon key liye quwat ka baais hain, aur bakriyan barkat wali hain, aur ghodon ki peshani key baalon sey qiyamat tak khair ka talluq qaaim kar diya gaya hai."
2306,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bakri jannat key janweron mein sey hai."
2307,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dolat mandon ko bakriyan paalney ka hukm diya aur naadaaron (ghareebon) ko murghiyan paalney ka hukm diya. aur farmaya : jab dolat mand murghiyan paalney lagen to Allah Taala bastiyon ko halak karney ka hukm dey deta hai."
